                        <p>费用与您的 Jetpack 套餐有关，按照您收益的百分比计算，从免费套餐的 10% 到 Creator 套餐的 2% 不等（含 Stripe 费用）。</p>','Transaction fees'=>'交易费','Unlimited subscribers'=>'订阅者数量无上限','100 subscribers'=>'100 名订阅者','Import a CSV file of your existing subscribers to be sent your Newsletter.'=>'导入现有订阅者的 CSV 文件，以便向其发送电子报。','Import subscribers'=>'导入订阅者','Monetize your online presence and earn from your website'=>'从您的线上形象中获利，并通过网站赚取收入','Grow your subscribers through our creator network and tools'=>'通过我们的创建者网络和工具增加订阅者数量','Create content that stands out'=>'创建与众不同的内容','product name shown in menuJetpack Manage'=>'Jetpack Manage','Jetpack Manage'=>'Jetpack Manage','IP address `%1$s` just failed is_usable_domain check as it is in the private network.'=>'IP 地址‘%1$s’刚刚未通过“is_usable_domain”检查，因为其位于私人网络上。','Generate text, tables, lists, and forms'=>'生成文本、表格、列表和表单','Unable to save new URL secret'=>'无法保存新的 URL 密钥','You do not have the correct user permissions to perform this action.'=>'您没有执行此操作的相应用户权限。','URL secret does not exist.'=>'URL 密钥不存在。','Upgrade'=>'升级','Priority support'=>'优先支持','Included'=>'包含','Severity labels'=>'严重性标签','Notifications'=>'通知','One-click auto fixes'=>'一键自动修复','Access to scan on Cloud'=>'访问云端扫描功能','Brute force protection'=>'强力保护','Automatic protection and rule updates'=>'自动保护和规则更新','Manual rules only'=>'仅限手动规则','Web Application Firewall'=>'Web 应用程序防火墙','Plus on-demand manual scans'=>'以及按需手动扫描','Daily automated scans'=>'每日自动扫描','Line by line malware scanning'=>'逐行恶意软件扫描','Check items against database'=>'根据数据库检查各项目','Scan for threats and vulnerabilities'=>'扫描威胁和漏洞','Generate text, tables, and lists'=>'生成文本、表格和列表','Jetpack AI Assistant brings the power of AI right into your WordPress editor, letting your content creation soar to new heights.'=>'Jetpack AI 助手将 AI 的强大功能引入您的 WordPress 编辑器，让您的内容创作提升到新的高度。','<p>Paid customers get dedicated email support from our world-class Happiness Engineers to help with any issue.</p>
						 <p>All other questions are handled by our team as quickly as we are able to go through the WordPress support forum.</p>'=>'<p>付费客户可以从我们优秀的快乐的工程师那里获得专门的电子邮件支持，帮助解决任何问题。</p>
						 <p>我们的团队会尽快通过 WordPress 支持论坛处理所有其他问题。</p>','Dedicated email support'=>'专门电子邮件支持','Deliver images from Jetpack\'s Content Delivery Network. Automatically resizes your images to an appropriate size, converts them to modern efficient formats like WebP, and serves them from a worldwide network of servers.'=>'通过 Jetpack 的内容交付网络交付图像。 自动将您的图像调整为适当的大小，将图像转换为现代化的高效格式（如 WebP），并通过全球服务器网络交付图像。','Image CDN'=>'图像 CDN','Discover and fix images with a suboptimal resolution, aspect ratio, or file size, improving user experience and page speed.'=>'发现并修复分辨率、宽高比或文件大小欠佳的图像，改善用户体验和页面速度。','Image guide'=>'图像指南','Run non-essential JavaScript after the page has loaded so that styles and images can load more quickly.'=>'加载页面后运行非必要的 JavaScript，以便可以更快加载样式和图像。','Defer non-essential JavaScript'=>'推迟加载非必要的 JavaScript','<p>It’s essential to regenerate Critical CSS to optimize your site speed whenever your HTML or CSS structure changes. Being on top of this can be tedious and time-consuming.</p>
								 <p>Boost’s cloud service can automatically detect when your site needs the Critical CSS regenerated, and perform this function behind the scenes without requiring you to monitor it manually.</p>'=>'<p>无论您的 HTML 或 CSS 结构何时发生变化，都必须重新生成关键 CSS 以优化您的站点速度。 掌控这些情况可能会很繁琐和耗时。</p>
								 <p>Boost 的云服务可以自动检测您的站点何时需要重新生成关键 CSS，并在后台执行此功能，而无需您手动监控。</p>','Automatic Critical CSS regeneration'=>'自动重新生成关键 CSS','<p>To enhance the speed of your site, with this plan you will need to optimize CSS by using the Manual Critical CSS generation feature whenever you:</p>
								<ul>
									<li>Make theme changes.</li>
									<li>Write a new post/page.</li>
									<li>Edit a post/page.</li>
									<li>Activate, deactivate, or update plugins that impact your site layout or HTML structure.</li>
									<li>Change settings of plugins that impact your site layout or HTML structure.</li>
									<li>Upgrade your WordPress version if the new release includes core CSS changes.</li>
								</ul>'=>'<p>如果使用此套餐，则为了提高站点的速度，您需要在以下情况下使用手动关键 CSS 生成功能来优化 CSS：</p>
								<ul>
									<li>更改主题。</li>
									<li>撰写新文章/页面。</li>
									<li>编辑文章/页面。</li>
									<li>启用、禁用或更新影响站点布局或 HTML 结构的插件。</li>
									<li>更改影响站点布局或 HTML 结构的插件的设置。</li>
									<li>如果新版本包含核心 CSS 更改，请升级 WordPress 版本。</li>
								</ul>','Manual Critical CSS regeneration'=>'手动重新生成关键 CSS','Move important styling information to the start of the page, which helps pages display your content sooner, so your users don’t have to wait for the entire page to load. Commonly referred to as Critical CSS.'=>'将重要的样式信息移至页面的开头，这有助于页面更快地显示您所需的内容，因此用户不必等待加载完整个页面。 通常被称为关键 CSS。','Starter Product FeatureComment & form spam protection'=>'评论和表单垃圾内容保护','Starter Product FeatureOne-click fixes for most threats'=>'一键修复大多数威胁','Starter Product FeatureReal-time cloud backups with 1GB storage'=>'实时云备份（1GB 存储空间）','Essential security tools: real-time backups and comment spam protection.'=>'必备安全工具：实时备份和评论垃圾内容保护。','Something went wrong. Please try again.'=>'出错了。 请重试。','Sorry, something is wrong with your Jetpack connection.'=>'抱歉，您的 Jetpack 连接出现问题。','Comprehensive site security, including VaultPress Backup, Scan, and Akismet Anti-spam.'=>'全面的站点安全性，包括 VaultPress Backup、Scan 和 Akismet Anti-spam。','Akismet Anti-spam'=>'Akismet Anti-spam','Jetpack VaultPress Backup'=>'Jetpack VaultPress Backup','Backup Product DisclaimerLearn more'=>'了解更多','Backup Product Disclaimer* Subject to your usage and storage limit.'=>'* 具体取决于您的使用和存储容量限制。','As always, feel free to <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact our support team</a> if you have any questions.'=>'和以往一样，如果您有任何疑问，请随时<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">联系我们的支持团队</a>。','<a href=\'%s\' target=\'_blank\' rel=\'noopener noreferrer\'>Learn more</a> about the connection owner and what will break if you do not have one.'=>'<a href=\'%s\' target=\'_blank\' rel=\'noopener noreferrer\'>详细了解</a>连接所有者，以及没有连接所有者时会中断的服务。','Connect to WordPress.com'=>'连接至 WordPress.com','Every Jetpack site needs at least one connected admin for the features to work properly. Please connect to your WordPress.com account via the button below. Once you connect, you may refresh this page to see an option to change the connection owner.'=>'每个 Jetpack 站点至少需要有一个已连接的管理员，