ng.'=>'%s 必须是一个字符串。','Activate'=>'启用','VideoPress Product FeatureUnlimited users'=>'用户数不受限','VideoPress Product FeatureAd-free and customizable player'=>'无广告、可定制的播放器','VideoPress Product FeatureBuilt into WordPress editor'=>'内置在 WordPress 编辑器中','VideoPress Product Feature1TB of storage'=>'1TB 的存储空间','Security Product FeatureComment & form spam protection'=>'垃圾评论和表单保护','Security Product FeatureOne-click fixes for most threats'=>'一键修复大多数威胁','Security Product FeatureAutomated real-time malware scan'=>'自动实时扫描恶意软件','Security Product FeatureReal-time cloud backups with 10GB storage'=>'实时云备份（10GB 存储空间）','Spelling correction'=>'拼写校正','Supports 38 languages'=>'支持 38 种语言','Powerful filtering'=>'强大的过滤器','Instant search and indexing'=>'即时搜索和编制索引','Help your site visitors find answers instantly so they keep reading and buying. Great for sites with a lot of content.'=>'帮助您的站点访客找到答案，以便他们可以继续阅读和购买。 非常适合内容丰富的站点。','Scan Product FeatureInstant email notifications'=>'即时电子邮件通知','Scan Product FeatureOne-click fixes for most issues'=>'一键修复大多数问题','Scan Product FeatureAutomated daily scanning'=>'每日自动扫描','Automatic scanning and one-click fixes keep your site one step ahead of security threats and malware.'=>'自动扫描和一键修复可让您的站点领先一步防范安全威胁和恶意软件。','You are not allowed to activate plugins on this site.'=>'您不能在此站点上激活插件。','Error activating Jetpack module'=>'启用 Jetpack 模块时遇到错误','Error activating Jetpack plugin'=>'启用 Jetpack 插件时遇到错误','Activation failed. Plugin is not installed'=>'启用失败。 未安装插件','Basic tools for a successful site'=>'打造成功站点所需的基本工具','Infinitely customizable with integrations and extensions'=>'通过集成和扩展程序可进行无限定制','Fully integrated with WordPress & WooCommerce'=>'与 WordPress 和 WooCommerce 完全集成','Manage billing and create invoices'=>'管理账单和创建发票','Manage unlimited contacts'=>'管理无限制的联系人','Standalone free plugin for those focused on speed'=>'独立免费插件，适用于注重速度的人员','Enable improvements in one click'=>'一键启用改进','Check your site performance'=>'检查您的站点性能','Backup Product FeatureOne-click restores'=